'''Zurah''' in [[Islamic cosmology]] is a pilgrimage that was originally built by [[Adam in Islam|Adam]]. It was lifted into the fourth level of [[Jannah]] during the time of [[Noah in Islam|Noah]] when [[The Flood]] occurred. It was the precursor to the [[Kaaba]].<ref name="Efendi1987">{{cite book|author=Caʻfer Efendi|title=Risāle-i Miʻmāriyye|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dJk3AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA49|accessdate=8 December 2014|year=1987|publisher=Brill Archive|isbn=90-04-07846-0|page=49}}</ref>

